OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1781853482
OL,3,CReform MP criticised for linking
OL,4,CEngland football wins to preventing
OL,5,Cabuse
OL,7,FA Reform UK MP has been criticised
OL,8,Fafter suggesting that England's
OL,9,Ffootball team needs to keep winning
OL,10,Fgames in the World Cup to prevent a
OL,11,Fspike in incidents of domestic abuse.
OL,13,FSarah Pochin, MP for Runcorn and
OL,14,FHelsby, made the claim in a short
OL,15,Fvideo message posted on social media
OL,16,Fthe day after England won their first
OL,17,FWorld Cup game 4-2 against Croatia.
OL,19,F"England won the football last night,
OL,20,Fand thank goodness they did," she said.
OL,26,@{D@AOU|D@]O]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/10
