OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,306,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30502
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1781853482
OL,3,CReform MP criticised for linking
OL,4,CEngland football wins to preventing
OL,5,Cabuse
OL,7,FPochin added: "Because on the
OL,8,Foccasions that England lose their
OL,9,Ffootball matches, the incidences of
OL,10,Fdomestic violence go through the roof.
OL,11,FSo boys, keep winning."
OL,13,FLeading charities which support
OL,14,Fdomestic abuse victims were among
OL,15,Fthose who criticised Pochin's remarks.
OL,26,@oD@OOUsD@WO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,306,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30503
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1781853482
OL,3,CReform MP criticised for linking
OL,4,CEngland football wins to preventing
OL,5,Cabuse
OL,7,FFarah Nazeer, chief executive of
OL,8,FWomen's Aid, said: "Football does not
OL,9,Fcause domestic abuse ` it is a choice
OL,10,Fthat is made by the abuser, time and
OL,11,Fagain, regardless of whether a team
OL,12,Fwins or loses a match.
OL,14,F"Research tells us that domestic abuse
OL,15,Fdoes rise during championships, but
OL,16,Fthis is the case whether the team wins
OL,17,For loses.
OL,26,@pD@TOUvD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,306,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30504
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1781853482
OL,3,CReform MP criticised for linking
OL,4,CEngland football wins to preventing
OL,5,Cabuse
OL,7,F"It is irresponsible to suggest that a
OL,8,Fteam's success is responsible for
OL,9,Fwhether a man commits domestic abuse
OL,10,For not.
OL,12,F"We also know that it is a pattern of
OL,13,Fbehaviour that repeats and escalates
OL,14,Fover time, and not something that
OL,15,Fhappens as a result of one match.
OL,17,F"Whether England wins, loses or draws,
OL,18,Fno woman or child should live in fear
OL,19,Fof that final whistle blow."
OL,26,@oD@AOUtD@AOUyD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,306,300,200,140,000,100
