OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1781853482
OL,3,CReform MP criticised for linking
OL,4,CEngland football wins to preventing
OL,5,Cabuse
OL,7,FA spokesperson for the charity Refuge
OL,8,Fsaid: "Refuge is deeply concerned by a
OL,9,Fhighly inappropriate social media post
OL,10,Ffrom Sarah Pochin MP suggesting that
OL,11,FEngland should win more men's football
OL,12,FWorld Cup matches to reduce domestic
OL,13,Fabuse.
OL,15,F"This is not only misleading, but
OL,16,Fcould allow perpetrators to evade
OL,17,Faccountability.
OL,26,@pD@GOUwD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,306,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30506
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1781853482
OL,3,CReform MP criticised for linking
OL,4,CEngland football wins to preventing
OL,5,Cabuse
OL,7,F"We must be clear: football is never
OL,8,Fan excuse for domestic abuse, and
OL,9,Fperpetrators cannot continue to be
OL,10,Fshielded by the myth that football
OL,11,Fdirectly causes abuse.
OL,13,F"While major sports tournaments can
OL,14,Fexacerbate pre-existing behaviours,
OL,15,Fabuse happens all year round, often
OL,16,Fhidden and unreported.
OL,26,@oD@AOUuD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,306,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30507
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1781853482
OL,3,CReform MP criticised for linking
OL,4,CEngland football wins to preventing
OL,5,Cabuse
OL,7,F"Abusers may use football or alcohol
OL,8,Fintake as an excuse, but there is
OL,9,Fnever any justification for domestic
OL,10,Fabuse. It is the abuser's actions
OL,11,Falone that are to blame ` not external
OL,12,Fevents or circumstances. It is a
OL,13,Fchoice, and it must be challenged.
OL,15,F"As the World Cup continues, it is
OL,16,Fmore vital than ever that we shift the
OL,17,Fnarrative and give domestic abuse the
OL,18,Fred card. To show your support for
OL,19,Fsurvivors, take action with Refuge
OL,20,Fnow."
OL,26,@oD@AOUwD@AOU|D@EO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/10
