OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1781853482
OL,3,CReform MP criticised for linking
OL,4,CEngland football wins to preventing
OL,5,Cabuse
OL,7,FPochin's political opponents also
OL,8,Fadmonished her for the video.
OL,10,FBridget Phillipson, the Education
OL,11,FSecretary and Minister for Women and
OL,12,FEqualities, wrote in response to
OL,13,FPochin: "Men should not beat up women.
OL,14,FFull stop. No excuses."
