OL,3,CReform MP criticised for linking
OL,4,CEngland football wins to preventing
OL,5,Cabuse
OL,7,FReform has come under fire in recent
OL,8,Fweeks for past social comments made by
OL,9,FRobert Kenyon, its candidate in the
OL,10,FMakerfield by-election.
OL,12,FKenyon used a now-deleted X account to
OL,13,Fsupport an offensive post about Welsh
OL,14,Fbroadcaster Carol Vorderman.
OL,16,FReform UK leader Nigel Farage has
OL,17,Fdismissed his candidate's past social
OL,18,Fmedia use as "a few laddish things",
OL,19,Fwhich were "posted a decade ago".
OL,26,@zD@NOUzD@cO]{D@LOU{D@`O]
